{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A world of books to explore!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Receive, sort, and organize the greatest classics of world literature the way you prefer! From Shakespeare to Flaubert, including Jules Verne and Machado de Assis: in Libritopia, you'll find all the must-have classics for any library!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/A_world_of_books_to_explore_V2.gif?t=1738262050\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Organize the space your way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Name your library, expand its size, and furnish the space! Set up the environment by placing shelves or using furniture to create corridors. Add labels to each shelf to classify books by genre, author, year, country, even color - or any other way you want! It\u2019s YOUR library.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/Organize_o_espa\u00e7o_do_seu_jeito.gif?t=1738262050\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Librarians unite!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Work with friends in multiplayer mode to manage the daily demands of your library. Divide tasks and collaborate to meet all the visitor's needs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3372420/extras/Bibliotec\u00e1rios_unidos!.gif?t=1738262050\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Keep an eye on the visitors!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ensure all visitors can access the books they want! Manage check-outs and book returns, assist visitors with finding books on the shelves, and make sure your library is a peaceful place. No cell phones allowed! Shhhhhh!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=